      KYLIE'S VALUES

      Clean
      Our formulas are designed with ingredients to ensure the right balance between efficiency, safety and responsibility, producing formulations that are more restrictive than regulations in the US, Canada, EU and beyond.
      Vegan
      We are vegan meaning that none of our products, packaging, formulas or ingredients contain animal derivatives or animal-by-products.
      Gluten Free
      We formulate without gluten-derived ingredients. While not proven to cause a reaction in those with gluten sensitivities, this is an extra commitment we take to be mindful of everyone's preferences.
      Cruelty Free
      We make skincare and makeup with love, for all. None of our products or formulas have or will ever be tested on animals.
      Paraben Free
      We formulate without parabens, a controversial preservative widely used in the cosmetics industry, because your safety and health is our priority.
